The target is a number that varies. The target is 1000.

A fruit is a kind of object.

A length is a kind of value. 1cm specifies a length.

An apple, a pear and an orange are fruits. A fruit has a length called size.

The size of a fruit is usually 10cm. The size of the apple is 7cm.

To begin:
	let the total raised be 900;
	showme the total raised;
	increase the total raised by 10;
	showme the total raised;
	increment the total raised;
	showme the total raised;
	decrease the total raised by 10;
	showme the total raised;
	decrement the total raised;
	showme the total raised;
	showme the target;
	increase the target by 10;
	showme the target;
	increment the target;
